      • processLinkAttributes

        protected WTCollection processLinkAttributes(ChangeItemIfc item,
                                             WTCollection binaryLinks)
                                      throws WTException
        Processes the ChangeRecord2 link for the resulting objects table. This implementation relies on the super class to process the common table attributes such as the comment and release target fields. Overriding this method should call this method instance to ensure proper handling of the binary link attributes.

        Supported API: true
        Overrides:
        processLinkAttributes in class RelatedProductDataFormDelegate
        Parameters:
        item - The change item
        binaryLinks - The collection of current binary links.
        Returns:
        A collection of just the "changed" binary links that are processed.
        Throws:
        WTException
